Name: Holy Advent : Archangel
Desc:
Unlocks all of your divine power for the advent of a higher power. Since the descended Archangels are too great, they manifest in the form of stone statues for a certain period of time
You can re-input the skill key with the down arrow key to summon the Archangels to your current location
If the Archangels hit an enemy using Damage Reflect, you will not take damage.
